    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and wear, but for the right buyer it represents a straightforward, cost-conscious opportunity for commuting, light use, or a project. Priced to deliver strong value and sold with clear, honest positioning.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great opportunity for someone who wants a cheap runaround, a first fixer-upper, or a handy project to tinker with. Priced to make sense and offered by someone who believes in being straight with buyers, it could be just the thing if you\u2019re after value and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC. Come have a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a tough, mechanical feel and plenty of upside. The engine fires up and pulls, transmission engages, and the chassis has the kind of straightforward, old-school serviceability enthusiasts appreciate. Not a perfect car, but it presents as complete and usable, with good bones for someone who wants affordable entry into ownership, a shop truck, or a weekend fixer that can be improved as you go. Priced to move for its condition while still reflecting its strong potential.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Rough around the edges, but usable and priced to move. First cash takes it.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Not every car tells a polished story\u2014some earn it mile by mile. This one has the kind of honest, road-worn character that makes it easy to imagine as a budget-friendly daily, a weekend project, or a practical extra set of keys for someone who values utility over flash. It carries itself with a certain grit and presence, offering a chance to get into something affordable with plenty of potential for the next owner to make it their own. If you appreciate vehicles with substance, simplicity, and room for a fresh chapter, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical low-cost option for someone seeking basic transportation, a starter project, or an extra set of wheels. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who appreciates value over cosmetics, but it still presents a solid opportunity at an approachable price. If you want an inexpensive vehicle with potential and room to make it your own, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    }
